Cell["\<\
Now, let us examine a lager system. Suppose that we are given a secrete bit \
string:\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1555491913,ExpressionUUID->"7c1a6d41-9c5b-440e-96bd-0b7ceea26df3"],

